com.wingman.client.plugin

Class PluginContainer

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.wingman.client.plugin.PluginContainer

  • public class PluginContainer
extends java.lang.Object
    PluginContainer is the base of the client-plugin layer, providing the client interactability with each and every plugin.
    It wraps a Plugin annotated Class.
